{"tid":1681624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最討厭真係班「偽黃」","createTime":"2019-10-29T14:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T07:25:19.000Z","uid":146828,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3e84440ad5789c4d48fc696447738159426c048","tid":1681624,"uid":146828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"藍固然之黑人憎<br />\n但班「偽黃」都一樣咁黑我憎<br />\n日撚日喺到屌人撐警 撐藍<br />\n但黨鐵照坐 藍店照食 360照買<br />\n(仲要藍店都排晒隊個下好嘢........)<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講要磨合期去適應 慢慢tune <br />\n721到而家已經3個幾月啦<br />\n仲要講到我堅持只食黃店好麻煩咁<br />\n係麻煩咗少少 但抗爭係咁㗎啦！<br />\n你哋班人幾時先肯齊心啲罷哂藍店藍户同黨鐵？"},{"pid":"aed8558fdff39d989347b8ffae368846099ae453","tid":1681624,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXEs9qi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXEs9qi.jpg&h=02cd3311&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"beadf3094e7b04a3c55c916e8694162b97b22826","tid":1681624,"uid":185057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"我以為你想講各打50大板既偽黃添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e81c4250f5bc59e83c87633bd6dc67ce31d54f","tid":1681624,"uid":158270,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:30:12.000Z","msg":"論抗爭者嘅心理，論政權利用抗爭者嘅心理，論抵抗非法逮捕嘅方式<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679866\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679866</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"46993769eb4a16fb00cd2c736476b147da0d71ba","tid":1681624,"uid":326414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T14:31:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"459d929610ad4032179c1c9be42feef78c2cbaac","tid":1681624,"uid":146828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46993769eb4a16fb00cd2c73647